{"tid":48733,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"考斜路停車係咪一定要拉手制入一波","createTime":"2016-12-21T08:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T15:56:05.000Z","uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5aa3833bf56f269068d323e469910076e2aed7c","tid":48733,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:54:55.000Z","msg":"求教"},{"pid":"acd58282659f5ae7e4a1c7ff5dacc83fc61afc65","tid":48733,"uid":46884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:57:05.000Z","msg":"手制空波喎"},{"pid":"112c986f0fceb4da80505e3b410c6db26d292466","tid":48733,"uid":53054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"駕駛學院：<br />\n上到斜佬 停車空波手制 <br />\n考官話開車 1波吊極力子比少少油鬆手制去"},{"pid":"a1100148366ccc8108ea1c73b1ba24de280d8b50","tid":48733,"uid":35536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"拉左手制入一波會死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以記呢個口訣 <br />\n手制空波 唔使諗咁多"},{"pid":"98db56eec7342023a936637cbc8a41c3a74296f4","tid":48733,"uid":41198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:04:56.000Z","msg":"同問係踩 踩brake 手制 空波？<br />\n開車就 入波 磨擦點 比少少油 鬆手制"},{"pid":"a931628a05084aab2ecad2ea9aaae93020a9e1e0","tid":48733,"uid":53054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉左手制入一波會死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以記呢個口訣 <br />\n手制空波 唔使諗咁多</blockquote><br />\n踩低極力子 入一波 吊住少少極力子就唔會架啦<br />\n放左手制先入一波我驚佢動作唔夠快會溜後"},{"pid":"e394827ce2210472552abc38c1de2b6c11544476","tid":48733,"uid":53054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問係踩 踩brake 手制 空波？<br />\n開車就 入波 磨擦點 比少少油 鬆手制</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我考哥時係踩break慢車 踩低哂極力子 踩break停定架車 入空波 拉手制 鬆break"},{"pid":"857a464d65ab6a51ea60a6787097e10679404d84","tid":48733,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駕駛學院：<br />\n上到斜佬 停車空波手制 <br />\n考官話開車 1波吊極力子比少少油鬆手制去</blockquote><br />\n停車手制空波丫 邊個教你咁失敗"},{"pid":"cbfc3bbfda6ea0ed48c1170be075c6d880221f27","tid":48733,"uid":34910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:26:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>駕駛學院：<br />\n上到斜佬 停車空波手制 <br />\n考官話開車 1波吊極力子比少少油鬆手制去</blockquote><br />\n停車手制空波丫 邊個教你咁失敗</blockquote><br />\n有分別嗎？停車踩低極力子已經同空波無分別"},{"pid":"88bdba16fe77b39a819fc2658f24b4388933b879","tid":48733,"uid":53054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>駕駛學院：<br />\n上到斜佬 停車空波手制 <br />\n考官話開車 1波吊極力子比少少油鬆手制去</blockquote><br />\n停車手制空波丫 邊個教你咁失敗</blockquote><br />\n有乜分別 做齊就得"},{"pid":"3a6df99038cf3ab56207d68287d62d693a64f934","tid":48733,"uid":64925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:33:09.000Z","msg":"乜香港考車咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳門要你係斜路入一波吊極力紙定住部車唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381bf0207c076f5a333254bdee55f4dedacb3acb","tid":48733,"uid":64925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜香港考車咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳門要你係斜路入一波吊極力<span style=\"color: red;\">子</span>定住部車唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace260a106f54e00e30ec3a2037744cb7a53496c","tid":48733,"uid":48075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:35:53.000Z","msg":"手掣空波<br />\n斜路平路泊車先手掣空波熄匙入一波"},{"pid":"ca8510b42ab6d86b7c760801d4ca96db00df4587","tid":48733,"uid":3995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:39:54.000Z","msg":"停車就手制空波<br />\n考完車熄埋匙嗰下先係入返一波"},{"pid":"764849498f44f50118216ee0f57b8f657f14550d","tid":48733,"uid":35536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉左手制入一波會死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以記呢個口訣 <br />\n手制空波 唔使諗咁多</blockquote><br />\n補充返，呢個係講緊斜路停車<br />\n唔係開車<br />\n<br />\n基本上好多巴打都有講<br />\n停車一定係 手掣空波"},{"pid":"75aed19d1412dcde6f8dcea1412f912e7d609a7d","tid":48733,"uid":46785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"停車手制空波<br />\n考車時，如果停車耐既話，手制唔入空波只踩極力子會比人TICK"},{"pid":"4d10bfcb50b63565dd71297257bc37d7789dd86b","tid":48733,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:04:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>駕駛學院：<br />\n上到斜佬 停車空波手制 <br />\n考官話開車 1波吊極力子比少少油鬆手制去</blockquote><br />\n停車手制空波丫 邊個教你咁失敗</blockquote><br />\n有乜分別 做齊就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空波手制有機會溜後<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fbd0988bfd83a9e90736680381bbc96805e1e6","tid":48733,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:10:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>駕駛學院：<br />\n上到斜佬 停車空波手制 <br />\n考官話開車 1波吊極力子比少少油鬆手制去</blockquote><br />\n停車手制空波丫 邊個教你咁失敗</blockquote><br />\n有乜分別 做齊就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空波手制有機會溜後<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你拉左手掣點溜後呀哥?<br />\n<br />\n除非你拉唔盡個手掣O者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22999440e6117a4d8808e83130e20f75eff491e6","tid":48733,"uid":41198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n有乜分別 做齊就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空波手制有機會溜後<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你拉左手掣點溜後呀哥?<br />\n<br />\n除非你拉唔盡個手掣O者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能佢空波個下無踩埋brake <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae780b189638e71a4c28546fa1b7a3bc6601b19b","tid":48733,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:03:04.000Z","msg":"你地兩位係唔係有d咩會錯意<br />\n燈位 停頓位<br />\n踩慢架車 差唔冇乜動力 or 架車開始震 踩極力子  空波拉手制 <br />\n開車 踩極力子 吊極力子 鬆手制 畀油去同時鬆極力子<br />\n<br />\n泊車<br />\n停車一樣 空波拉手制 熄匙 上斜平路入一波 落斜泊車入後波<br />\n <br />\n係唔係想問呢d"},{"pid":"0997666235003e71fe2a6f58e6f881dc0a1c825e","tid":48733,"uid":40423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:20:33.000Z","msg":"如果停完車考官叫你熄匙你就要入返個一波或者後波,就咁停車既話拉手掣之後入空波"},{"pid":"7543b94e6048c6e6687e0f90c1633356aa0b0310","tid":48733,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"即係考路試時上緊斜停車都唔洗入一波?"},{"pid":"8bc9f3fc15741aa9f538d43bd8dbf1fde0bcf687","tid":48733,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n停車手制空波丫 邊個教你咁失敗</blockquote><br />\n有乜分別 做齊就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空波手制有機會溜後<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識唔識架你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢撚事答你"},{"pid":"917dd747e977731d7f2c3fa33588012c9dcd6434","tid":48733,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空波手制有機會溜後<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你拉左手掣點溜後呀哥?<br />\n<br />\n除非你拉唔盡個手掣O者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能佢空波個下無踩埋brake <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線架，慢慢落brake，夠咁上下慢踩低極力子<br />\n踩到最低，右腳brake唔鬆keep住，拉手制，入空波，再放曬兩隻腳<br />\n唔係咁樣順序架咩，次序錯咪柒左囉"},{"pid":"a6d4e117712e25dc6b7fa53a3aff7d88725f3c84","tid":48733,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:40:09.000Z","msg":"師傅教係要入一波或者後波再加手制去鎖死部車喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}